# 📱 IncuLink – iOS App for Connecting Startups with Incubation Centres

IncuLink is an innovative iOS application built using **SwiftUI** and **UIKit**, developed as part of a brainstorming-based training project. The app is designed to create a collaborative digital bridge between **early-stage startups** and **incubation centers**, helping founders discover, connect, and grow their ventures through incubation support.

> 🚀 _Developed during iOS Developer Training using Swift & Apple development best practices._

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ **Startup Onboarding** – Register and create detailed startup profiles.
- ✅ **Incubation Centre Listing** – Browse verified incubators with support details.
- ✅ **Smart Matchmaking** – Find relevant incubators based on startup domain.
- ✅ **Real-Time Request System** – Send and manage collaboration/invitation requests.
- ✅ **Smooth UI/UX** – Native iOS feel built with a blend of SwiftUI and UIKit.
- ✅ **Login/Signup Flow** – Secure and intuitive onboarding experience.

---

## 🧠 Project Objective

The aim was to address the **lack of centralized access to incubation support** in India and globally by leveraging a user-centric mobile platform. The idea stemmed from a team brainstorming activity focused on **real-world problem-solving using digital solutions**.

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Component          | Technology        |
|-------------------|-------------------|
| Language           | Swift             |
| UI Framework       | SwiftUI & UIKit   |
| State Management   | @State, @Binding  |
| Data Handling      | Local JSON Mock (future Firebase integration planned) |
| IDE                | Xcode             |
| Platform           | iOS 15+           |

---

## 🚧 Future Improvements

- Integrate Firebase or Supabase for backend & real-time data
- Chat feature between startup and incubator
- Admin approval workflow for incubator onboarding
- Personalized dashboard for startups
- Push notifications for updates

